        "gg6uIDISuu8_text": "Results, Reported by Real Users:",
        "gg9mt8SYjhb_text": "<p><strong>Day 1:</strong> Skin feels cooler, soothed, and noticeably hydrated</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 3:</strong> Glow begins to emerge — some users even skip foundation</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 7:</strong> Fine lines appear softened, and skin feels firmer, bouncier, and well-rested</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now, many busy women are using it&nbsp;<strong>just twice a week </strong>— no layering, no guesswork, just visible results.</p>",
        "gg8P26fUryi_label": "<p>GET YOURS NOW</p>"
      }
